From 0000000000000000000000000000000000000000 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: wosnxn123 <wosnxn123@users.noreply.github.com>
Date: Mon, 6 Jul 2026 01:30:00 +0800
Subject: [PATCH] Add Vanilla-like experience config

Adds config/canvas-server.yml toggles restoring vanilla mechanics that
Paper/Folia changed.

vanilla-like-experience.enabled: master toggle for 17 vanilla mechanics
(tripwire string farms, TNT/sand duping, permanent block break, headless
pistons, vanilla mob spawning, unlimited entity collisions, player
cramming, vanilla phantom/insomnia, no TNT limit, vanilla
hopper/bee/item-merge/end-portal teleport). Ported from Lophine 0048.

old-feature.old-zombie-reinforcement / old-leader-zombie-health:
INDEPENDENT per-feature toggles (NOT tied to vanilla-like-experience),
matching Lophine's OldFeatureConfig structure (separate config section
with per-feature static booleans). Ported from Lophine 0013 (zombie
reinforcement spawns plain ZOMBIE) + 0014 (skip leader zombie setHealth).
Default false.

Patch regenerated via git diff on Canvas main applied source (correct
blob index + context). The OldFeature Part class itself lives in
GlobalConfiguration.java (canvas-server/src/main/java), not in this patch.

